{%- render 'section-spacing-collapsing' -%}

{%- comment -%}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CSS

SEN Feeding Journey — stage panel. Per build-brief Section 5.2.
ONE section file, expected to be added 4 times to /pages/sen-feeding-journey
(one per ability-based stage: just-starting-out, finding-grip, building-confidence,
eating-independently).

CRITICAL DESIGN RULE (CLAUDE.md + brief 5.0):
NO age labels anywhere in this section. Stage identity is via stage_id (anchor) and
heading/sub-heading copy only. Progress is celebrated, not measured against timelines.

Layout per panel:
- H2 stage headline + H3 sub-headline
- Body copy (2–3 sentences, empathetic)
- "Signs your child might be here" — 4 observation bullets (not checklists)
- Celebration / encouragement line — standout styling
- "Find the right tools →" CTA button
- 3-cell UGC community photo grid
- Family quote block (pull-quote + attribution)
- OT quote block (quote + name + role + 2 trust labels)
- Product grid: 3–5 products, OT-recommended highlighted (server-side via 'ot-recommended' tag)
- Next-stage teaser card (hidden when next_heading and next_body are both blank)

Anchor contract: emits id="{stage_id}" on the <sen-stage-panel> custom element.
Matches sen-hero.liquid's pill anchors.

Impact v6.9.1 conventions:
- Section-scoped CSS variables under #shopify-section-{{ section.id }}
- Custom element wrapper <sen-stage-panel> with explicit display:block
- No reveal-on-scroll attributes
- Image_tag with widths array; lazy loading on product and UGC images

v1 deferrals (polish list):
- Add-to-bag on product cards (currently links to PDP only)
- Variant display on product cards (shows product.title only)
- Real UGC image upload flow — for now image_picker per cell, optional
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}

<style>
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
    --sen-panel-bg: {{ section.settings.panel_bg.rgb }};
    --sen-panel-padding-d: {{ section.settings.padding_d }}px;
    --sen-panel-padding-m: {{ section.settings.padding_m }}px;
    --sen-panel-accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color.rgb }};
    --sen-panel-heading-color: {{ section.settings.heading_color.rgb }};
    --sen-panel-heading-size: {{ section.settings.heading_size_m }}px;
    --sen-panel-sub-size: {{ section.settings.sub_heading_size_m }}px;
    --sen-panel-body-size: {{ section.settings.body_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-signs-size: {{ section.settings.signs_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-celebration-size: {{ section.settings.celebration_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-quote-size: {{ section.settings.family_quote_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-ot-quote-size: {{ section.settings.ot_quote_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-product-img-size: {{ section.settings.product_img_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-product-name-size: {{ section.settings.product_name_size }}px;
    --sen-panel-product-price-size: {{ section.settings.product_price_size }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} {
      --sen-panel-heading-size: {{ section.settings.heading_size_d }}px;
      --sen-panel-sub-size: {{ section.settings.sub_heading_size_d }}px;
    }
  }

  /* Wrapper */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel {
    display: block;
    background-color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-bg));
    padding: var(--sen-panel-padding-m) var(--container-gutter);
    scroll-margin-top: var(--header-height, 0);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel {
      padding: var(--sen-panel-padding-d) var(--container-gutter);
    }
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__inner {
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Heading + sub-heading */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__heading {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-2);
    font-family: var(--heading-font-family);
    font-weight: var(--heading-font-weight);
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-heading-size);
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__sub-heading {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-4);
    font-family: var(--heading-font-family);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-sub-size);
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
  }

  /* Body */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__body {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-8);
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-body-size);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.85);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  /* Signs block */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__signs-label {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-3);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__signs {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-8);
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-3);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__signs {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__sign {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--spacing-3) var(--spacing-4) var(--spacing-3) var(--spacing-8);
    background: rgb(var(--doddl-color-bg));
    border-radius: var(--rounded);
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-signs-size);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__sign::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: var(--spacing-4);
    top: var(--spacing-3);
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Celebration line */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__celebration {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-8);
    padding: var(--spacing-5) var(--spacing-6);
    background: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent) / 0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
    border-radius: 0 var(--rounded) var(--rounded) 0;
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-celebration-size);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  /* CTA */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__cta-row {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-10);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 999px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__cta-row .button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* UGC grid */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__ugc {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-3);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-10);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__ugc-cell {
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: rgb(var(--doddl-color-bg));
    border-radius: var(--rounded);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__ugc-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__ugc-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.4);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-3);
  }

  /* Quotes — family + OT */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quotes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-5);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-10);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quotes {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: var(--spacing-6);
    }
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote {
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--spacing-6);
    background: rgb(var(--doddl-color-bg));
    border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
    border-radius: 0 var(--rounded) var(--rounded) 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote-text {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-3);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote--family .sen-panel__quote-text {
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-quote-size);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote--ot .sen-panel__quote-text {
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-ot-quote-size);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote-attr {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote-name {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__quote-role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.7);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__trust-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: var(--spacing-3) 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--spacing-2);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__trust-pill {
    padding: 2px 10px;
    background: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.06);
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.7);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: var(--rounded-full);
  }

  /* Products */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__products-label {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-4);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__products {
    display: grid;
    grid-auto-flow: column;
    grid-auto-columns: 65vw;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__products::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__products {
      grid-auto-flow: row;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
      grid-auto-columns: auto;
      overflow: visible;
    }
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product {
    position: relative;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    border-radius: var(--rounded);
    padding: var(--spacing-3);
    background: rgb(var(--background-primary));
    transition: border-color 200ms ease;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product.is-ot-recommended {
    border-color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__ot-badge {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--spacing-2);
    right: var(--spacing-2);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
    color: white;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: var(--rounded-full);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product.is-ot-recommended .sen-panel__ot-badge {
    display: block;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product-link {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: rgb(var(--doddl-color-bg));
    border-radius: var(--rounded-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product-name {
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-1);
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-product-name-size);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__product-price {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--sen-panel-product-price-size);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgb(var(--doddl-color-primary));
  }

  /* Empty placeholder */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__placeholder {
    padding: var(--spacing-10) var(--spacing-6);
    border: 2px dashed rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.18);
    border-radius: var(--rounded);
    text-align: center;
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.55);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__placeholder code {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    background: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.06);
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: var(--rounded-xs);
  }

  /* Next-stage teaser */
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-4);
    padding: var(--spacing-5);
    background: rgb(var(--doddl-color-bg));
    border-radius: var(--rounded);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgb(var(--sen-panel-accent));
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-content {
    flex: 1 1 200px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-label {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.55);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-heading {
    margin: 2px 0 var(--spacing-1);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgb(var(--sen-panel-heading-color));
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-body {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgb(var(--text-primary) / 0.7);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .sen-panel__next-cta {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
</style>

{%- comment -%}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LIQUID
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign stage_id = section.settings.stage_id | default: 'sen-stage' | handle -%}
{%- assign collection_handle = section.settings.collection -%}
{%- assign stage_collection = collections[collection_handle] -%}

<div {% render 'section-properties' %}>
  <sen-stage-panel class="sen-panel" id="{{ stage_id }}">
    <div class="sen-panel__inner">
      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2 class="sen-panel__heading">{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.sub_heading != blank -%}
        <p class="sen-panel__sub-heading">{{ section.settings.sub_heading | escape }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.body != blank -%}
        <p class="sen-panel__body">{{ section.settings.body | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Signs (4 observation bullets) {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- assign has_sign = false -%}
      {%- for n in (1..4) -%}
        {%- assign s_key = 'sign_' | append: n -%}
        {%- if section.settings[s_key] != blank -%}{%- assign has_sign = true -%}{%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}

      {%- if has_sign -%}
        {%- if section.settings.signs_label != blank -%}
          <p class="sen-panel__signs-label">{{ section.settings.signs_label | escape }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}
        <ul class="sen-panel__signs" role="list">
          {%- for n in (1..4) -%}
            {%- assign s_key = 'sign_' | append: n -%}
            {%- assign s_value = section.settings[s_key] -%}
            {%- if s_value != blank -%}
              <li class="sen-panel__sign">{{ s_value | escape }}</li>
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Celebration line {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if section.settings.celebration != blank -%}
        <p class="sen-panel__celebration">{{ section.settings.celebration | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} CTA {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if section.settings.cta_label != blank -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__cta-row">
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_url | default: stage_collection.url | default: '#' }}"
             class="button button--xl">
            {{- section.settings.cta_label | escape -}}
          </a>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} 3-cell UGC grid {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- assign has_ugc = false -%}
      {%- for n in (1..3) -%}
        {%- assign u_key = 'ugc_' | append: n -%}
        {%- if section.settings[u_key] != blank -%}{%- assign has_ugc = true -%}{%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}

      {%- if has_ugc -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__ugc">
          {%- for n in (1..3) -%}
            {%- assign u_key = 'ugc_' | append: n -%}
            {%- assign u_alt_key = 'ugc_' | append: n | append: '_alt' -%}
            {%- assign ugc_image = section.settings[u_key] -%}
            {%- assign ugc_alt = section.settings[u_alt_key] -%}
            <div class="sen-panel__ugc-cell">
              {%- if ugc_image != blank -%}
                {{- ugc_image
                    | image_url: width: ugc_image.width
                    | image_tag:
                        loading: 'lazy',
                        sizes: '(max-width: 999px) 33vw, 280px',
                        widths: '200,300,400,500,600,800',
                        alt: ugc_alt,
                        class: 'sen-panel__ugc-img' -}}
              {%- else -%}
                <div class="sen-panel__ugc-placeholder">UGC photo {{ n }}</div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Family + OT quote pair {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if section.settings.family_quote != blank or section.settings.ot_quote != blank -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__quotes">
          {%- if section.settings.family_quote != blank -%}
            <blockquote class="sen-panel__quote sen-panel__quote--family">
              <p class="sen-panel__quote-text">{{ section.settings.family_quote | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
              {%- if section.settings.family_attr != blank -%}
                <div class="sen-panel__quote-attr">
                  <cite class="sen-panel__quote-name">{{ section.settings.family_attr | escape }}</cite>
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </blockquote>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if section.settings.ot_quote != blank -%}
            <blockquote class="sen-panel__quote sen-panel__quote--ot">
              <p class="sen-panel__quote-text">{{ section.settings.ot_quote | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
              {%- if section.settings.ot_name != blank or section.settings.ot_role != blank -%}
                <div class="sen-panel__quote-attr">
                  {%- if section.settings.ot_name != blank -%}
                    <cite class="sen-panel__quote-name">{{ section.settings.ot_name | escape }}</cite>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if section.settings.ot_role != blank -%}
                    <span class="sen-panel__quote-role">{{ section.settings.ot_role | escape }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if section.settings.trust_1 != blank or section.settings.trust_2 != blank -%}
                <ul class="sen-panel__trust-list" role="list">
                  {%- if section.settings.trust_1 != blank -%}
                    <li class="sen-panel__trust-pill">{{ section.settings.trust_1 | escape }}</li>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if section.settings.trust_2 != blank -%}
                    <li class="sen-panel__trust-pill">{{ section.settings.trust_2 | escape }}</li>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </ul>
              {%- endif -%}
            </blockquote>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Product grid (3–5) {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if stage_collection != blank and stage_collection.products.size > 0 -%}
        {%- if section.settings.products_label != blank -%}
          <p class="sen-panel__products-label">{{ section.settings.products_label | escape }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__products" role="list">
          {%- for product in stage_collection.products limit: 5 -%}
            {%- assign is_ot = false -%}
            {%- if product.tags contains 'ot-recommended' -%}{%- assign is_ot = true -%}{%- endif -%}
            <div class="sen-panel__product{% if is_ot %} is-ot-recommended{% endif %}" role="listitem">
              <span class="sen-panel__ot-badge" aria-hidden="true">OT pick</span>
              <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="sen-panel__product-link">
                <div class="sen-panel__product-image">
                  {%- if product.featured_image != blank -%}
                    {{- product.featured_image
                        | image_url: width: product.featured_image.width
                        | image_tag:
                            loading: 'lazy',
                            sizes: '(max-width: 999px) 65vw, 18vw',
                            widths: '200,300,400,500,600,800',
                            class: 'sen-panel__product-img' -}}
                  {%- else -%}
                    {{- 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'sen-panel__product-img' -}}
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
                <p class="sen-panel__product-name">{{ product.title | escape }}</p>
                <p class="sen-panel__product-price">{{ product.price | money }}</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      {%- else -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__placeholder">
          {%- if collection_handle != blank -%}
            <p>
              Products will appear here once the
              <code>{{ collection_handle | escape }}</code>
              collection is created in Shopify.
            </p>
          {%- else -%}
            <p>Products will appear here once a collection is selected in the section settings.</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- comment -%} Next-stage teaser — hidden when no heading/body set (so eating-independently can omit) {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- if section.settings.next_heading != blank or section.settings.next_body != blank -%}
        <div class="sen-panel__next">
          {%- if section.settings.next_icon != blank -%}
            <span class="sen-panel__next-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ section.settings.next_icon | escape }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
          <div class="sen-panel__next-content">
            {%- if section.settings.next_label != blank -%}
              <p class="sen-panel__next-label">{{ section.settings.next_label | escape }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.next_heading != blank -%}
              <p class="sen-panel__next-heading">{{ section.settings.next_heading | escape }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.next_body != blank -%}
              <p class="sen-panel__next-body">{{ section.settings.next_body | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
          {%- if section.settings.next_cta != blank and section.settings.next_url != blank -%}
            <a href="{{ section.settings.next_url }}" class="button button--lg sen-panel__next-cta">
              {{- section.settings.next_cta | escape -}}
            </a>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </sen-stage-panel>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "SEN journey — stage panel",
  "class": "shopify-section--sen-stage-panel",
  "tag": "section",
  "disabled_on": {
    "templates": ["password"],
    "groups": ["header", "custom.overlay"]
  },
  "settings": [
    { "type": "paragraph", "content": "Critical rule: NO age labels anywhere — in the heading, sub-heading, body, signs, or next-stage teaser. SEN progress is celebrated, not measured against timelines." },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Stage identity" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "stage_id", "label": "Stage anchor ID",
      "info": "Used as the HTML anchor on this panel (#{value}). Must match the matching pill anchor in the SEN hero. Use lowercase, hyphenated.",
      "default": "just-starting-out"
    },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Heading" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "heading", "label": "Stage headline (H2)", "default": "Just starting out" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "sub_heading", "label": "Sub-headline (H3)", "default": "Every journey begins somewhere" },
    { "type": "range", "id": "heading_size_d", "label": "Heading size — desktop", "min": 22, "max": 44, "step": 2, "unit": "px", "default": 32 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "heading_size_m", "label": "Heading size — mobile", "min": 18, "max": 38, "step": 2, "unit": "px", "default": 26 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "sub_heading_size_d", "label": "Sub-heading size — desktop", "min": 16, "max": 28, "step": 1, "unit": "px", "default": 20 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "sub_heading_size_m", "label": "Sub-heading size — mobile", "min": 14, "max": 24, "step": 1, "unit": "px", "default": 17 },
    { "type": "color", "id": "heading_color", "label": "Heading colour", "default": "#3D157D" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "accent_color", "label": "Accent colour", "info": "Tints sub-heading, sign bullets, celebration line, quote borders, OT-pick border, and the next-stage teaser icon. Defaults to doddl aqua.", "default": "#30BEAA" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Body" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "body", "label": "Body copy", "info": "2–3 sentences, empathetic tone. No age references." },
    { "type": "range", "id": "body_size", "label": "Body size", "min": 13, "max": 19, "step": 1, "unit": "px", "default": 15 },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Signs (4 observation bullets — not a checklist)" },
